#. Max bytes: 376
msgctxt "Offset_0x560_Len_376"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"October, 1995. Kamurocho, one of Asia's largest entertainment districts.\n"
"In this town swirling with desire and violence lived a yakuza by the\n"
"name of Kazuma Kiryu, a Lieutenant Advisor of the prestigious Dojima Family.\n"
"\n"
"But he was better known as \"The Dragon of Dojima.\"\n"
"\n"
"He was a rising star, and soon he would take control over a family\n"
"of his own...\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Ottobre 1995. Kamurocho, il quartiere dei divertimenti più grande dell'Asia.\n"
"In questa città di desiderio e violenza viveva uno yakuza di\n"
"nome Kazuma Kiryu, Tenente Consigliere della prestigiosa Famiglia Dojima.\n"
"\n"
"Era meglio noto come \"Il Drago di Dojima\".\n"
"\n"
"Un astro nascente, pronto a prendere la guida di una famiglia\n"
"tutta sua...\n"
"\n"

#. Max bytes: 504
msgctxt "Offset_0x8D0_Len_504"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"At Kiryu's side was his best friend, Akira Nishikiyama.\n"
"The two grew up together in Sunflower Orphanage and swore\n"
"their oaths to the Tojo Clan's Dojima Family on the same day.\n"
"\n"
"The pair was often joined by Yumi Sawamura, another of\n"
"Sunflower's orphans, whom they treated like a younger sister.\n"
"\n"
"The happy days where the three of them would get together and drink\n"
"at the upscale bar, Serena, are some of Kiryu's fondest memories...\n"
"\n"
"But one stormy night, their lives changed forever."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Al fianco di Kiryu c'era il suo migliore amico, Akira Nishikiyama.\n"
"I due crebbero insieme nell'Orfanotrofio Girasole e giurarono\n"
"fedeltà alla Famiglia Dojima del Clan Tojo lo stesso giorno.\n"
"\n"
"A loro si univa spesso Yumi Sawamura, un'altra orfana del\n"
"Girasole, che trattavano come una sorella minore.\n"
"\n"
"I giorni in cui i tre si ritrovavano a bere al lussuoso\n"
"bar Serena sono tra i ricordi più cari di Kiryu...\n"
"\n"
"Ma una notte di tempesta, le loro vite cambiarono per sempre."

#. Max bytes: 652
msgctxt "Offset_0xD50_Len_652"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"The Patriarch of the Dojima Family, Sohei Dojima, kidnapped Yumi,\n"
"prompting Nishikiyama to shoot him in a blind frenzy.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu arrived at the scene to find Nishikiyama still holding the\n"
"smoking gun, and Kiryu made a fateful decision: In order to ensure\n"
"Nishikiyama could still be around for his ill sister, Kiryu took\n"
"the gun in hand and sent both Nishikiyama and Yumi out of the building. \n"
" \n"
"That day, Kiryu became a patriarch killer, a crime above all crimes\n"
"in the criminal world of the yakuza.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu was jailed and expelled from the organization, and Yumi,\n"
"suffering from traumatic memory loss, disappeared from the hospital."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Il Patriarca della Famiglia Dojima, Sohei Dojima, rapì Yumi,\n"
"spingendo Nishikiyama a sparargli in un attimo di follia.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu giunse sulla scena trovando Nishikiyama con ancora in mano\n"
"la pistola fumante. Prese quindi una decisione fatale: per far sì che\n"
"l'amico potesse restare accanto alla sorella malata, prese l'arma\n"
"e fece fuggire sia Nishikiyama che Yumi dall'edificio.\n"
"\n"
"Quel giorno Kiryu divenne l'assassino del suo patriarca, il crimine\n"
"supremo nel mondo criminale della yakuza.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu fu incarcerato ed espulso dall'organizzazione e Yumi,\n"
"affetta da amnesia traumatica, scomparve dall'ospedale."

#. Max bytes: 451
msgctxt "Offset_0x12E0_Len_451"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Ten years passed...\n"
"December, 2005. Kiryu emerges from prison to a changed world.\n"
"\n"
"Nishikiyama had lost his sister and suffered greatly in the\n"
"ten years, and as a result, had twisted into a monster,\n"
"obsessed with power and climbing the ranks of the Tojo Clan.\n"
"\n"
"Not even Shintaro Kazama, Patriarch of the Kazama Family and\n"
"founder of Sunflower Orphanage, a father figure to them both,\n"
"could stay Nishikiyama's dark transformation."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Dieci anni dopo...\n"
"Dicembre 2005. Kiryu esce e trova un mondo cambiato.\n"
"\n"
"Persa la sorella, Nishikiyama aveva sofferto molto in\n"
"quel decennio, diventando un mostro ossessionato dal potere\n"
"e dalla scalata ai vertici del Clan Tojo.\n"
"\n"
"Nemmeno Shintaro Kazama, Patriarca della Famiglia Kazama\n"
"e fondatore del Girasole, un padre per entrambi,\n"
"poté fermare l'oscura trasformazione di Nishikiyama."

#. Max bytes: 575
msgctxt "Offset_0x1770_Len_575"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"In a meeting of the Tojo Clan's direct patriarchs, Nishikiyama,\n"
"now patriarch of his own family, exposed the fact that ten billion\n"
"yen had been stolen from the clan's coffers.\n"
"\n"
"In the ensuing chaos, the Tojo Clan's third chairman, Masaru Sera,\n"
"was murdered, and an assassination attempt was made on Kazama right\n"
"before Kiryu's eyes.\n"
"\n"
"And as the Tojo Clan crumbled, Goro Majima, the Mad Dog of Shimano,\n"
"began to play in the ashes.\n"
"\n"
"The conflict nearly escalated into a civil war, and the shadow of\n"
"the Nishikiyama Family loomed large over the incident..."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"In una riunione dei patriarchi del Clan Tojo, Nishikiyama,\n"
"ora patriarca della sua famiglia, svelò che dieci miliardi di yen\n"
"erano stati rubati dalle casse del clan.\n"
"\n"
"Nel caos generale, il terzo presidente Masaru Sera\n"
"fu ucciso, e Kazama subì un attentato davanti agli occhi di Kiryu.\n"
"\n"
"Mentre il Clan Tojo andava in pezzi, Goro Majima, il Cane Pazzo di\n"
"Shimano, iniziò a giocare tra le ceneri.\n"
"\n"
"Il conflitto sfiorò la guerra civile e l'ombra della Famiglia\n"
"Nishikiyama incombeva sull'incidente..."

#. Max bytes: 499
msgctxt "Offset_0x20E0_Len_499"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"The girl's name was Haruka Sawamura.\n"
"\n"
"Despite being only nine years old, she came to Kamurocho herself in\n"
"hopes of finding her mother, Mizuki. Like Kiryu, Haruka too had grown\n"
"up in Sunflower Orphanage, and her Aunt Yumi had entrusted her\n"
"with a pendant said to be \"worth ten billion yen.\"\n"
"\n"
"The criminal underworld was drawn to the girl and the pendant like moths\n"
"to a flame. Kamurocho became engulfed in conspiracy and betrayal,\n"
"with Nishikiyama at the heart of the conflict.\n"
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Il nome della bambina era Haruka Sawamura.\n"
"\n"
"Pur avendo solo nove anni, giunse a Kamurocho da sola nella\n"
"speranza di trovare sua madre, Mizuki. Come Kiryu, anche Haruka\n"
"era cresciuta al Girasole, e sua zia Yumi le aveva affidato\n"
"un ciondolo che si diceva \"valesse dieci miliardi di yen\".\n"
"\n"
"La malavita fu attratta dalla ragazzina e dal ciondolo come falene\n"
"dalla luce. Kamurocho fu avvolta da complotti e tradimenti,\n"
"con Nishikiyama al centro del conflitto.\n"

#. Max bytes: 595
msgctxt "Offset_0x2530_Len_595"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu and Haruka finally caught up to Kazama, who was able to explain\n"
"the whole truth of the incident.\n"
"\n"
"Haruka was in fact, Yumi's daughter. Mizuki was simply Yumi's alias,\n"
"created to protect her from a politician by the name of Kyohei Jingu.\n"
"\n"
"Not only did the Tojo Clan's missing funds actually belong to Jingu,\n"
"but he was also Haruka's father. Jingu had manipulated the Tojo Clan from\n"
"the shadows in an effort to dispose of his scandalously illegitimate daughter.\n"
"\n"
"In an effort to chip away at his power, Kazama, Yumi, and Sera had teamed up\n"
"to steal his ten billion yen."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu e Haruka riuscirono a rintracciare Kazama, il quale spiegò\n"
"l'intera verità sull'incidente.\n"
"\n"
"Haruka era in realtà la figlia di Yumi. Mizuki era solo un alias\n"
"di Yumi, creato per proteggerla dal politico Kyohei Jingu.\n"
"\n"
"I fondi scomparsi del Clan Tojo non solo appartenevano a Jingu,\n"
"ma lui era anche il padre di Haruka. Jingu aveva manipolato il\n"
"clan dall'ombra per sbarazzarsi della sua scomoda figlia illegittima.\n"
"\n"
"Per tentare di indebolire il suo potere, Kazama, Yumi e Sera si\n"
"erano alleati per sottrargli quei dieci miliardi di yen."

#. Max bytes: 503
msgctxt "Offset_0x2A60_Len_503"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"To reclaim his money, Jingu singled out Nishikiyama's ambition to become\n"
"the successor to the late Sera and used that as a means to an end. The\r\n"
"two both stood to gain, as Nishikiyama would become the fouth chairman.\n"
"\n"
"However, the Tojo Clan's true successor was written in the secret will\n"
"of Sera, with Kazama as its witness: None other than Kazuma Kiryu. \n"
"\n"
"Declaring this to Jingu, Kiryu crushed him and his entire special\n"
"forces unit, and then settled the score with Nishikiyama."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Per riavere i soldi, Jingu sfruttò l'ambizione di Nishikiyama\n"
"di succedere al defunto Sera. Entrambi avevano da guadagnarci,\n"
"poiché Nishikiyama sarebbe diventato il quarto presidente.\n"
"\n"
"Tuttavia, il vero successore del Clan Tojo era scritto nel\n"
"testamento segreto di Sera, di cui Kazama era testimone:\n"
"nessun altro se non Kazuma Kiryu.\n"
"\n"
"Rivelato ciò a Jingu, Kiryu annientò lui e la sua intera unità di\n"
"forze speciali, per poi chiudere i conti con Nishikiyama."

#. Max bytes: 412
msgctxt "Offset_0x2EF0_Len_412"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"An explosion rocked the Millennium Tower where the money had been held.\n"
"As money fluttered into the streets, the people who Kiryu cared about more\n"
"than anyone in the world breathed their last.\n"
"\n"
"Yumi, who shielded Kiryu from a bullet fired by Jingu.\n"
"\n"
"Nishikiyama, who in his final moments smiled at Kiryu as he ignited\n"
"the bomb to take accountability for his actions and end the bloodshed..."
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Un'esplosione scosse la Millennium Tower, dove si trovava il denaro.\n"
"Mentre i soldi piovevano per strada, le persone a cui Kiryu\n"
"teneva di più al mondo esalarono l'ultimo respiro.\n"
"\n"
"Yumi, che fece da scudo a Kiryu contro un proiettile di Jingu.\n"
"\n"
"Nishikiyama, che alla fine sorrise a Kiryu mentre innescava\n"
"la bomba per pagare le sue colpe e fermare il massacro..."

#. Max bytes: 303
msgctxt "Offset_0x3260_Len_303"
msgid ""
"The Events of Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"In that moment of despair, Kiryu lost his will to go on. But there in\n"
"front of him was Haruka, now the only living legacy of Yumi, the woman\n"
"he'd come to love.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu took Haruka's hand. The Dragon of Dojima and the \"Girl Worth\n"
"Ten Billion Yen\" took their first steps together... \n"
msgstr ""
"Gli eventi di Yakuza\n"
"\n"
"Nella disperazione, Kiryu perse la forza di andare avanti.\n"
"Ma davanti a lui c'era Haruka, l'unica eredità in vita di Yumi,\n"
"la donna che amava.\n"
"\n"
"Kiryu le prese la mano. Il Drago di Dojima e la \"Ragazza\n"
"da dieci miliardi\" fecero il primo passo insieme...\n"

